Package: scoremodel
Type: Package
Title: Credit Scoring Modeling Toolbox
Version: 0.2.1
Author: hongfa.zhong
Maintainer: hongfa.zhong <944860176@qq.com>
Description: A set of flexible, efficient and easy to use functions to build a credit scoring model from beginning to end, including dataset reading and preprocessing, variable binning and woe-encoding, model performance and stability validation, as well as visualization.
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: RColorBrewer, ROCR, caret, data.table, dplyr, ggplot2, gridExtra, pROC, parallel, plotROC, plyr, psych, showtext (>= 0.5), smbinning, vcd, grDevices, graphics, stats, broom, utils, sysfonts (>= 0.7.1)
Suggests: devtools, roxygen2, testthat (>= 0.11.0), tidyverse, knitr, rmarkdown, rpart
License: GPL (>= 2) | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
